---
title: Super Cheesy Chicken Melts with roast root veg and garlicky greens
description: This recipe features chicken topped with rich tomato paste, chilli flakes and plenty of cheese! The slight sweetness and acidity from the tomato works a treat with the melted cheese, while the simple and delish veg accompaniments do their part to make this a nutritionally balanced meal.
